high_descs: Turn right to walk into the dining room to reach the fridge on the left.
Pick up the mug from the fridge.
Turn around to reach the microwave.
Put the mug in the microwave.
Turn around to exit the dining room and walk right to face the sofa.
Pick up the mug from the couch.
Turn around to walk to the dining room on the left to reach the microwave on the left.
Put the mug next to the other mug in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put two Mug in the Microwave.

high_descs: Turn right go past the dining table to the fridge.
Open the refrigerator door and pick up the mug on the shelf.
Turn around to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the mug in the microwave.
Head toward the doorway to the sofa.
Pick up the mug from the sofa.
Head back to the microwave.
Open the microwave door and place the mug in the microwave behind the other mug, close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Place the mugs in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right, then go straight towards the two doors and enter the one on the left, heading towards the fridge in the corner.
Take out the mug from the fridge.
Turn around to the microwave.
Place the mug in the microwave.
Leave the room the way you came in, then head towards the large sofa on the right.
Pick up the mug.
Head back to the microwave.
Place the mug into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place two mugs into a microwave.
